{"tid":2378304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"開電視。權謀風暴 。吹奏青年上大灣區","createTime":"2021-01-24T11:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T10:52:08.000Z","uid":137789,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"80a18630cbd0f6748920f2026c191479ec475469","tid":2378304,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:02:40.000Z","msg":"香港啲青年真係上去就戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n啱啱頭先播完，香港啲免費電視遲啲係咪只可以播呢啲仆街節目？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府一直強調，大灣區充滿發展機遇，近年亦有唔少人到大灣區發展。工業界立法會議員吳永嘉認為，年青人應該到大灣區多嘗試，營造機會，希望香港能夠融入內地內循環發展大局。佢會同為正策士嘅年青成員互相分享看法！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkopentv/videos/2875714936040586\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkopentv%2Fvideos%2F2875714936040586&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=c2e4bd0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkopentv/videos/2875714936040586</a>"},{"pid":"7186cf84c05012a78ec2c18cb9737645c1f82e73","tid":2378304,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:06:20.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"cd9da53797cf9bfd9fb35d9d79f92b8f616cb705","tid":2378304,"uid":59919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T10:52:08.000Z","msg":"藍絲圍爐節目"}]}